\f0\fs28 \cf2 \cb3 \expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
We've gotten a feel for how users behave inside AI Mode. They accept the shortlist, pick the top result, and click nothing else.\
\
What I keep wondering is whether the same user behaves the same way when an AI Overview shows up inside a normal Google SERP. Same person, different surface. Does the acceptance carry over?\
\
I dug into a new clickstream study of 846k US Google sessions from Feb and March 2026 to find out. Short version: the behavior reverses. The user who accepts in AI Mode starts comparing, back-scrolling, and re-reading the moment an AIO lands on a regular SERP. The meta description and title tag are doing more work than they have in 18 months.\
\
Drops Tuesday (not tomorrow, because of Memorial Day).}
